MAIN RESPONSIBILITIES
Design and implement new components or enhancements to existing components;
Work with analysts, architects and software engineers to define and deliver quality technical solutions that meet requirements;
Act as a mentor and share knowledge with the team;
Find solutions to the most complex problems;
Recognize and adapt to frequent changes in priorities and direction as business needs evolve.
PROFILE REQUIRED
You have experience in front-end development, particularly web development, and have a strong background in React or Vue.js;
You take initiative and challenge the status quo to improve existing processes and the product itself;
You are willing to contribute to knowledge sharing within the team to help other developers grow;
You understand the importance of constant communication with stakeholders, to showcase the evolution of your team's work;
You pay particular attention to the performance and speed of different implementations.
